2026-05-04T00:38:51.3245857Z 13    <!--
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3246378Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3247185Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3248334Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
