2026-05-04T00:38:51.3254702Z 22    <!--
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3255240Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3255915Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3256541Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3257291Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3258006Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3258685Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3259406Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3260156Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3260858Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3261521Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3262147Z 33    -->
2026-05-04T00:38:51.3262728Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
